- **End every turn with ONE `ChatResponse` call.** `ChatResponse` IS your reply. Never call other tools after it; never call it in parallel with another tool (the parallel one ships a placeholder that overrides nothing). Never emit a status echo / one-liner / placeholder ("Workflow has completed with failure", "I'll look into it"). The user already sees status — `ChatResponse.message` must carry the *analysis*.
